[[Image:Shimane-kawamoto-town.png|thumb|Location of Kawamoto in Shimane prefecture]]
{{nihongo|'''Kawamoto'''|<U+5DDD><U+672C><U+753A>|Kawamoto-machi}} is a [[towns of Japan|town]] located in [[<U+014C>chi District, Shimane|<U+014C>chi District]], [[Shimane Prefecture|Shimane]], [[Japan]].

As of 2003, the town has an estimated [[population]] of 4,513 and a [[population density|density]] of 42.42 persons per km<U+00B2>. The total area is 106.39 km<U+00B2>.

